data.description:
Welcome to your dream horse property nestled on a serene 10-acre parcel, accessible via a private road. This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bath home built in 2005 offers a perfect blend of modern comforts and the tranquility of country living.

If you're looking for a peaceful retreat where your horses can roam freely and you can enjoy the comforts of a modern home, this property is a must-see.
